&lt;p&gt;We’re partnering with &lt;strong&gt;a leading not-for-profit home care provider&lt;/strong&gt; that delivers essential services to older Australians in regional areas. With the aged care sector shifting rapidly and competition increasing, this organisation is focused on ensuring clients and families clearly see the value of their care and choose to trust them on their journey.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;They’re now seeking&lt;strong&gt; Customer Service Officer &lt;/strong&gt;to join their growing team!&lt;/p&gt;
